data.name: FontEmphasis
desc: Determines the type and position of an emphasis mark in Asian texts.

items.name: DOT_ABOVE
lines: a dot is set above (or right from vertical text) the text.

items.name: CIRCLE_ABOVE
lines: a circle is set above (or right from vertical text) the text.

items.name: DISK_ABOVE
lines: a disc is set above (or right from vertical text) the text.

items.name: ACCENT_ABOVE
lines: an accent is set above (or right from vertical text) the text.

items.name: DOT_BELOW
lines: a dot is set below (or left from vertical text) the text.

items.name: CIRCLE_BELOW
lines: a circle is set below (or left from vertical text) the text.

items.name: DISK_BELOW
lines: a disk is set below (or left from vertical text) the text.

items.name: ACCENT_BELOW
lines: an accent is set below (or left from vertical text) the text.
